,"side":"RIGHT","in_reply_to_id":1388463611,"original_position":6,"position":6,"subject_type":"line"},"pull_request":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/pulls/52073","id":1591876078,"node_id":"PR_kwDOABkWpM5e4hnu","html_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/52073","diff_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/52073.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/52073.patch","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/52073","number":52073,"state":"open","locked":false,"title":"Add a hashtable to lookup method roots","user":{"login":"BioTurboNick","id":1438610,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0Mzg2MTA=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1438610?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/BioTurboNick","html_url":"https://github.com/BioTurboNick","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BioTurboNick/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BioTurboNick/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BioTurboNick/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BioTurboNick/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BioTurboNick/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BioTurboNick/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BioTurboNick/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BioTurboNick/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BioTurboNick/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"body":"This PR implements a hash table for looking up method roots. Compression and uncompression of methods with many roots should be sped up, removing a barrier to adding additional roots (such as to address #41099, #50082).

Currently, each time a root is added, all previous roots have to be checked, leading to O(n^2) runtime. The hash table adds minimal memory overhead for each method (as a hidden field) to convert this step to O(n). The table is implemented with the existing `htable_t` type, using `jl_object_id` as the hash function and `jl_egal` as the equality function.

Some notes:
* I was hesitant to try fully replacing the roots list, which is a Julia array visible in Julia, since the hash table is a C type.
* There is a condition where the roots list can be populated without the hash table being generated; I'm not sure where, currently I just generate the table ad hoc if necessary
* I'm using `malloc_s` to create the hash table, but I'm not sure if there are other places to free it. I saw `jl_gc_managed_malloc`, but was unsure if it was okay to use.
* Wasn't sure how to bring in the `jl_` functions to `egalhash` with the files located in `support/`, maybe there's a better arrangement.
* Could empirically find an optimal switch point between simple iteration and initializing the hash table
* Sysimage (sys.so) size before: 129.7 MB; after: 130.2 MB
* Compilation of Base + Stdlibs ~10% faster (n = 2, YMMV)","created_at":"2023-11-08T05:37:24Z","updated_at":"2023-11-09T19:03:38Z","closed_at":null,"merged_at":null,"merge_commit_sha":"b697300aa17692c7edce7c666698d66873b981f3","assignee":null,"assignees":[],"requested_reviewers":[],"requested_teams":[],"labels":[],"milestone":null,"draft":true,"commits_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/pulls/52073/commits","review_comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/pulls/52073/comments","review_comment_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/pulls/comments{/number}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/52073/comments","statuses_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/statuses/22ff8a4d580ec626fc72d5b4abd2ae95ca8a88e5","head":{"label":"BioTurboNick:roots-htable","ref":"roots-htable","sha":"22ff8a4d580ec626fc72d5b4abd2ae95ca8a88e5","user":{"login":"BioTurboNick","id":1438610,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0Mzg2MTA=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1438610?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/BioTurboNick","html_url":"https://github.com/BioTurboNick","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BioTurboNick/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BioTurboNick/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BioTurboNick/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BioTurboNick/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BioTurboNick/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BioTurboNick/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BioTurboNick/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BioTurboNick/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BioTurboNick/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"repo":{"id":217130235,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnkyMTcxMzAyMzU=","name":"julia","full_name":"BioTurboNick/julia","pri